nodes.text: This individual was a female Ugnaught who served in the Galactic Republic as an analyst.

During the Clone Wars, she was assigned on Republic Mobile Surgical Unit 12 on the planet of Drongar. She was in charge of analyzing the bota crop being harvested. When she learned that the potency of the bota was slowly weakening, she passed the information to Rorand Zuzz, a male Ugnaught who claimed that she was physically attracted to him.
